description: Tommy rides alone, but he takes a jump too fast and his mustang tosses him to the ground. Milan is nearby and races to see if his new heartthrob is OK. He starts to massage Tommy's leg and before long his massage works up to the crotch. Tommy is so turned on that he forgets the pain and these two cowboys throw off their clothes and let their mutual desires run wild. Milan takes charge and fucks Tommy right there in the field.
title: Au Natural: Bareback Ranchers 2
